                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7565" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1191</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2402 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">涅槃重生，恒康医疗破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Nirvana Reborn,the bankruptcy reorganization road Of Hengkang Medical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王鹏，邓海龙，钟慧兰，张海雪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新里程健康科技集团股份有限公司（曾用名：恒康医疗集团股份有限公司）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；恒康医疗；府院联动；联合投资人</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bankruptcy reorganization;Hengkang Medical;Linkage between the government and the court;Joint Investors</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着国家鼓励社会资本举办医疗机构，许多医药企业便开始采用并购的方式进入医疗服务行业，恒康医疗便是靠着“车轮式”并购获得了“民营医院第一股”的美誉。但由于其激进式的扩张战略，导致资产负债率高达97.98%，被债务人申请破产重整。本案例以恒康医疗破产重整事件为主线，叙述了恒康医疗从诞生、上市到陷入债务困境，最后经过破产重整涅槃重生的全过程，着重描述了陇南中院如何在缺乏经验的情况下，充分发挥府院联动模式的优势，采用独特的管理人“1+1”模式与“投资人联合体”形式，帮助恒康医疗成功重整、扭亏为盈的过程。案例旨在帮助学生熟悉破产重整程序，思考如何根据实际情况选择合适的管理人与投资人，恒康医疗背负巨额负债最终成功重整的案例对诸多深陷债务危机濒临破产的企业有着很强的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the country encourages social capital to set up medical institutions, many medical enterprises begin to enter the medical service industry through mergers and acquisitions. Hengkang Medical has won the reputation of &quot;the first stock of private hospitals&quot; by virtue of &quot;wheel type&quot; mergers and acquisitions. However, due to its aggressive expansion strategy, its asset-liability ratio reached 97.98%, and its debtor applied for bankruptcy reorganization. This case takes the bankruptcy reorganization event of Hengkang Medical as the main line, narrating the whole process of Hengkang Medical from its birth, listing to its debt predicament, and finally its rebirth through bankruptcy reorganization. It focuses on how Longnan Middle Hospital gives full play to the advantages of the linkage mode of government and hospital, and adopts the unique management mode of &quot;1+1&quot; and the form of &quot;investor consortium&quot; under the circumstances of lack of experience. Help Hengkang Medical successful restructuring, turnaround process. The case aims to help students get familiar with the bankruptcy reorganization process and think about how to choose the right manager and investors according to the actual situation. The successful reorganization of Hengkang Medical with huge debts has a strong reference significance for many enterprises in debt crisis and on the verge of bankruptcy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购；破产重整；SWOT分析模型；公司战略与风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
